Family Weekend SurveyAll families that registered to attend Family Weekend 2023 were sent an email with a link to complete a survey. We appreciate your time and look forward to hearing from you.
If you attended Family Weekend and did not receive a link to complete the survey, please email familyweekend@stanford.edu and we will send you a link to share your feedback.
